modName: Evil Incarnate Daedric Gear by Omniel
summary: Daedric Armor Inspired by Alduin Textures and a hate for the people of Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
**This is a Re-texture**

Well this is my first attempt at going from zero knowledge in modding/skinning to actually doing it. What inspired me to start this little project were the Alduin body textures I found when I was browsing bsa\'s. I imported them into photoshop (I have experience with photoshop) and starting messing around trying to create a set of daedric armor based off of parts of his body and this is what I got. I don\'t want it to look exactly like Alduin I wanted to create my own version on daedric armor just using his textures. I been working on this as much as I can and I personally think it is coming along really well, I hope you enjoy it and if you don\'t sit in front of a mirror and cry about it.



To install: Unpack the \"Textures\" file into the Skyrim/Data folder.
author: Omniel Machia
